IV) IFFCheck

   SYNTAX: IFFCheck <iff file name>

   IFFCheck checks the integrity of any IFF file.

   A typical listing looks like this:

--- Checking file "pic:life/pumpkin"---
 FORM 6194 ILBM
. BMHD 20
. CMAP 96
. CRNG 8
. CRNG 8
. CRNG 8
. CRNG 8
. BODY 5985
--- (IFF_OKAY) A good IFF file.

